msgid "Lightning Struck"
msgstr "雷霆降临"

msgid ""
"Ashkore continues to antagonize the sky world.  Please defeat him and bring "
"me his Electrite."
msgstr ""
"阿什科尔仍在不断挑衅天空世界。请击败它，并把它的雷晶带给我。"

msgid "Ashkore is not a creature to be trifled with.  Exercise caution."
msgstr ""
"阿什科尔不是可以轻视的敌人。务必小心。"

msgid ""
"This will do for now, but I will need more Electrite tomorrow.  Bring me "
"enough, and you will be rewarded."
msgstr ""
"这些暂时够用了，但明天我还需要更多雷晶。带来足够的数量，你就会得到奖励。"

msgid "Tell Hugo you have the Electrite."
msgstr ""
"告诉雨果你已经拿到了雷晶。"

msgid "Thank you.  I suspect you will make good use of this item."
msgstr ""
"谢谢你。我想你会善加利用这件物品。"
